com.sk89q.intake

Interface Description

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SettableDescription

    public interface Description
    A description of a command, providing information on the command's parameters, a short description, a help text, and usage information. However, it is up for implementations to provide the information — some implementations may provide very little information.

    This class does not define a way to execute the command. See CommandCallable, which has a getDescription() method, for an interface that does define how a command is executed.
